</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
[[Image:Assembly3_SketchSkeleton-08.png|300px|link=]] [[Image:Button_right.svg|16px|link=]] [[Image:Assembly3_SketchSkeleton-09.png|300px|link=]]
