</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
And this kinematic (sub-)chain ends with a [[Image:Assembly_ConstraintPointOnLine.svg‎‎|16px]] [[Assembly3_ConstraintPointOnLine|Point on line]] constraint, too.
